Sentencas: Direct internal reforming of methanol is applied as fuel for a Ni-YSZ anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with a flat tube based on double-sided cathodes.
Titulo: Durability of direct internal reforming of methanol as fuel for solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: It achieves a power density (PD) of 0.25 W/cm(2) at 0.8 V, reaching about 90% of that is fueled by H-2.
Titulo: Durability of direct internal reforming of methanol as fuel for solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: And the cell has been operated for more than 120 h by the direct internal reforming of methanol.
Titulo: Durability of direct internal reforming of methanol as fuel for solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: The durability and apparent advantage for using humidified methanol may lead to widespread applications by direct internal reforming method for this new designed SOFC in the future.
